<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Toplantƒ± √ñzeti</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #673ab7, #9575cd);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }
        
        .summary-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f3e5f5, #e1bee7);
            border: 2px solid #673ab7;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .summary-header h2 {
            color: #4527a0;
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .meeting-info {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #673ab7;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        
        .meeting-info h3 {
            color: #673ab7;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .info-item {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .info-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #555;
            min-width: 120px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        
        .info-value {
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .section {
            margin: 25px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        
        .notes-section {
            background: #e3f2fd;
            border: 1px solid #2196f3;
        }
        
        .tasks-section {
            background: #e8f5e8;
            border: 1px solid #4caf50;
        }
        
        .section h4 {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .notes-section h4 {
            color: #1976d2;
        }
        
        .tasks-section h4 {
            color: #2e7d32;
        }
        
        .note-item, .task-item {
            background: white;
            padding: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-left: 3px solid;
        }
        
        .note-item {
            border-left-color: #2196f3;
        }
        
        .task-item {
            border-left-color: #4caf50;
        }
        
        .note-meta, .task-meta {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }
        
        .task-assignee {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #e8f5e8;
            color: #2e7d32;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .task-priority {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-left: 5px;
        }
        
        .priority-low { background: #e8f5e8; color: #2e7d32; }
        .priority-normal { background: #fff3e0; color: #f57c00; }
        .priority-high { background: #ffebee; color: #d32f2f; }
        .priority-critical { background: #f3e5f5; color: #7b1fa2; }
        
        .statistics {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 20px 0;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .stat-card {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            flex: 1;
            margin: 0 5px 10px 5px;
            min-width: 120px;
        }
        
        .stat-number {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #673ab7;
        }
        
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
            
            .info-item {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }
            
            .info-label {
                min-width: auto;
                margin-bottom: 5px;
            }
            
            .statistics {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            
            .stat-card {
                margin: 5px 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üìä Toplantƒ± √ñzeti</h1>
            <p><%= companyName %></p>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <!-- Summary Header -->
            <div class="summary-header">
                <h2>üìã Toplantƒ± Tamamlandƒ±</h2>
                <p>Toplantƒ± √∂zeti ve alƒ±nan kararlar a≈üaƒüƒ±da yer almaktadƒ±r</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Meeting Information -->
            <div class="meeting-info">
                <h3><%= meeting.baslik %></h3>
                
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">üóìÔ∏è Tarih:</span>
                    <span class="info-value"><%= meetingDate %></span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">‚è±Ô∏è S√ºre:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">
                        <%= duration !== 'Belirsiz' ? duration + ' dakika' : 'Belirsiz' %>
                    </span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">üë• Katƒ±lƒ±mcƒ±:</span>
                    <span class="info-value"><%= participantCount %> ki≈üi</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Statistics -->
            <div class="statistics">
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-number"><%= notes.length %></div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Not</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-number"><%= tasks.length %></div>
                    <div class="stat-label">G√∂rev</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-number"><%= participantCount %></div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Katƒ±lƒ±mcƒ±</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-number">
                        <%= duration !== 'Belirsiz' ? duration : '?' %>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Dakika</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Meeting Notes -->
            <% if (notes && notes.length > 0) { %>
            <div class="section notes-section">
                <h4>üìù Toplantƒ± Notlarƒ±</h4>
                <% notes.forEach(function(note) { %>
                <div class="note-item">
                    <div><%= note.icerik %></div>
                    <div class="note-meta">
                        <% if (note.olusturan) { %>
                        üë§ <%= note.olusturan.ad %> <%= note.olusturan.soyad %>
                        <% } %>
                        ‚Ä¢ üïí <%= new Date(note.tarih).toLocaleString('tr-TR') %>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <% }); %>
            </div>
            <% } %>

            <!-- Tasks Created -->
            <% if (tasks && tasks.length > 0) { %>
            <div class="section tasks-section">
                <h4>üìã Olu≈üturulan G√∂revler</h4>
                <% tasks.forEach(function(task) { %>
                <div class="task-item">
                    <div style="font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 5px;">
                        <%= task.baslik %>
                    </div>
                    <% if (task.aciklama) { %>
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: #666;">
                        <%= task.aciklama %>
                    </div>
                    <% } %>
                    <div class="task-meta">
                        <% if (task.atananKullanici) { %>
                        <span class="task-assignee">
                            üë§ <%= task.atananKullanici.ad %> <%= task.atananKullanici.soyad %>
                        </span>
                        <% } %>
                        <% if (task.oncelik) { %>
                        <span class="task-priority priority-<%= task.oncelik %>">
                            <%= task.oncelik.toUpperCase() %>
                        </span>
                        <% } %>
                        <% if (task.teslimTarihi) { %>
                        <br>üìÖ Teslim: <%= new Date(task.teslimTarihi).toLocaleDateString('tr-TR') %>
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <% }); %>
            </div>
            <% } %>

            <!-- No Content Messages -->
            <% if ((!notes || notes.length === 0) && (!tasks || tasks.length === 0)) { %>
            <div style="background: #f5f5f5; border-radius: 5px; padding: 20px; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
                <p style="color: #666; margin: 0;">
                    üìù Bu toplantƒ±da not veya g√∂rev olu≈üturulmamƒ±≈ütƒ±r.
                </p>
            </div>
            <% } %>

            <!-- Important Note -->
            <div style="background: #e3f2fd; border: 1px solid #2196f3; border-radius: 5px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <p style="margin: 0; color: #1976d2;">
                    <strong>üí° Bilgi:</strong> 
                    Bu √∂zet toplantƒ± tamamlandƒ±ktan sonra otomatik olarak olu≈üturulmu≈ütur. 
                    G√∂revlerin durumu sistem √ºzerinden takip edilebilir.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong><%= companyName %></strong></p>
            <p>Bu √∂zet otomatik olarak olu≈üturulmu≈ütur.</p>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999;">
                Toplantƒ± tamamlanma tarihi: <%= new Date().toLocaleString('tr-TR') %>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>